=Description=

"Join us and explore Regen Network’s new CarbonPlus Credit - an innovative ecosystem service credit with co-benefits including carbon sequestration, animal welfare, soil health and grasslands health. In this webinar we’ll review the current state of carbon credit markets as well as the methodologies and technology supporting the CarbonPlus Credit.

Panelists include Regen Network CEO Christian Shearer, Toby Grogan from ImpactAg, Julie Mettenburg from Tall Grass Network and James Pittman, Senior Ecological Economist for Regen Network. Moderated by David Fortson, Director of Marketing for Regen Network & CEO of LOACOM."

